import React, { Component } from 'react'
import NavDropdown from 'react-bootstrap/NavDropdown'

import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'
const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <Nav className="justify-content-center"
        
        justify variant="tabs"
        
            onSelect={(selectedKey) => (selectedKey)}
            
        >
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="/cart">SHOP</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="/AddNewCart">Добавить товар</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="/ChangeCart">Редактировать товар товар</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>

            <NavDropdown title="Личный кабинет" id="nav-dropdown" >
        <NavDropdown.Link href="/login">Action</NavDropdown.Link>
        <NavDropdown.Link eventKey="4.2">Another action</NavDropdown.Link>
       
      </NavDropdown>


            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="/login">Войти в аккаунт</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="/home">Выйти</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>

        </Nav>
    );
};
export default Navbar;
